大桥在被正式命名以前，常用“三桥”或“大西洋侧大桥”来指代<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.centralamericadata.com/en/article/home/Third_Bridge_Over_Canal_to_be_Tendered_in_August|title=Third Bridge Over Canal to be Tendered in August|date=2012-03-28|publisher=CentralAmericaData|language=en|access-date=2015-07-17|archive-date=2019-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190607075021/https://www.centralamericadata.com/en/article/home/Third_Bridge_Over_Canal_to_be_Tendered_in_August|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.panama-guide.com/article.php/20120327134916877|title=Construction Of Third Bridge Over Panama Canal in Colon Will Start in October 2012|date=2012-03-27|publisher=Panama Guide|language=en|access-date=2015-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612210621/http://www.panama-guide.com/article.php/20120327134916877|archive-date=2018-06-12|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。大桥于2013年1月开始施工，原计划工期3年半，2016年中完工<ref name="vinci" />，但截至2016年12月，预计完工日期已推迟到2018年中<ref>{{cite web|title=Autoridad del Canal de Panamá, 31 de diciembre de 2016|url=http://micanaldepanama.com/ampliacion/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/20161231-Pte-Atlantico.pdf|publisher=Autoridad del Canal de Panamá|date=2016-12-31|language=es|access-date=2018-01-07|archive-date=2018-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180107175232/http://micanaldepanama.com/ampliacion/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/20161231-Pte-Atlantico.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2019年8月2日，大桥正式举行竣工通车典礼<ref>{{cite web |title=巴拿马运河三桥竣工通车 |url=http://panama.mofcom.gov.cn/article/jmxw/201908/20190802887501.shtml |publisher=中华人民共和国驻巴拿马共和国大使馆经济商务参赞处 |date=2019-08-03 |access-date=2019-08-18 |archive-date=2019-08-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190818123800/http://panama.mofcom.gov.cn/article/jmxw/201908/20190802887501.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

